content: Amen.I think the last time I watched that brain drain was an episode where Kim was lamenting in her drawn out nasal whine, the deeper questions of the universe, such as whether the kale in her $35.00 salad at The Ivey, “would, like, miss the feta, if she ordered it, like, on the side.”The greater question Ezinne Ukoha, is why and how I still know that. Ahhh.
